description:
Davey and Teddy are sent to Principal Denny's office for tardiness, but to their surprise Principal Denny is understanding, not harsh. 

Directed by Art Clokey, Raymond Peck
Starring Hal Smith, Dick Beals, Norma MacMillan

Cast
Hal Smith as Goliath
Dick Beals as David 'Davey' Hansen
Norma MacMillan as Davey Hansen 
Nancy Wible as Sally Hansen
Ginny Tyler as Elaine Hansen
